des:
Brighten up your dull and monotonous day with some fun filled one-liners sure to leave you in splits. New Content added every month. This skill is guaranteed to tell you a new joke every time you ask Alexa to churn one out from Joke Machine. Be sure to fire it up whenever you feel like because hey it takes 26 muscles to smile but 62 to frown :)

PS: Contains Epic One Liner Sarcastic Comebacks for you to use on your unsuspecting friends.
